videos.description: Clemson converts in the red zone as QB Trevor Lawrence throws over the middle to find Tee Higgins for a 14-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence gets Clemson on the board with TD pass) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Lawrence gets Clemson on the board with TD pass

videos.description: Clemson RB Travis Etienne runs up the gut and carries multiple defenders into the end zone for a 14-yard score.
videos.headline: Etienne powers into end zone

videos.description: Clemson punter Will Spiers can't handle the snap, allowing Wake Forest to take over deep in Clemson territory.
videos.headline: Clemson botches punt

videos.description: Bella Martina attends a Clemson game after receiving fanfare for her TikTok videos showing her likeness to Tigers QB Trevor Lawrence.
videos.headline: Lawrence look-alike attends Clemson game

videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence throws a perfect pass to the end zone and finds Tee Higgins for a 14-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence throws dime to Higgins for 2nd TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Lawrence throws dime to Higgins for 2nd TD

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence and Tee Higgins show off their chemistry as Lawrence hits Higgins for a 30-yard score, the pair's third touchdown connection of the half.

videos.headline: Lawrence, Higgins connect for 3rd TD of 1st half

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence zips a pass to Frank Ladson Jr. in the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown, putting Clemson ahead 38-3.
